Installation instructions for EINSfit-py
========================================

For EINSfit, the following versions are required:
    Python: 3.6 or higher
    NumPy: 1.16 or higher
    lmfit: 0.9.13 or higher
    matplotlib: 2.0 or higher
    cycler: 0.10 or higher (normally included in matplotlib)
    
    
RECOMMENDED INSTALLATION with pip:  
-------------------------
To install the EINSfit Python module with pip, use:
    python setup.py sdist
    pip install .dist/EINSfit-***VERSION***.tar.gz
     
To uninstall use:
    pip uninstall EINSfit
    
-------------------------
-------------------------


NOT RECOMMENDED INSTALLATION but works:
---------------------------------------
To install the EINSfit Python module in a fast way with easy_install, use:

    python setup.py build
    python setup.py install
    
---------------------------------------
---------------------------------------
  

